#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmymoney; Settings"
msgstr "Configuração do &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:14
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings described below modify the behavior of &kmymoney;, allowing "
#| "you to customize it to meet the needs of your unique financial affairs, "
#| "and to modify its look and feel to match your personality. These settings "
#| "can be changed through <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
#| "menu item or by using the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo>. In order for any changes "
#| "to take effect the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button must be clicked."
msgid ""
"The settings described in this chapter modify the behavior of &kmymoney;, "
"allowing you to customize it to meet the needs of your unique financial "
"affairs, and to modify its look and feel to match your personality. These "
"settings can be changed through the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item "
"or by using the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo>. In order for any changes to take effect the "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button must be clicked."
msgstr ""
"As configurações descritas abaixo modificam o comportamento do &kmymoney;, "
"permitindo-lhe personalizá-lo de acordo com as necessidades dos seus "
"assuntos pessoais únicos, e para modificar a sua aparência e comportamento "
"de acordo com a sua personalidade. Estas opções podem ser modificadas "
"através de <menuchoice><guimenu>Configuração</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configurar o &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"ou usando a combinação de teclas <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>Shift</keycap> <keycap>,</keycap></keycombo>. Para que as "
"alterações façam efeito, deve carregar no botão <guibutton>Aplicar</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:25
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the left of the settings dialog is a list of icons and labels, each "
#| "representing a particular area of the program. When you click on one of "
#| "those icons, the right part of the dialog will display controls for "
#| "configuring that area of the program, often divided into several tabs."
msgid ""
"On the left of the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> or settings dialog is a "
"list of icons and labels, each representing a particular area of the "
"program. When you click one of those icons, the right part of the dialog "
"will display controls for configuring that area of the program, often "
"divided into several tabs."
msgstr ""
"À esquerda da janela de configuração existe uma lista de ícones e legendas, "
"cada uma delas representando uma área em particular do programa. Quando "
"carregar num desses ícones, a parte à direita da janela irá mostrar "
"controlos para configurar essa área do programa, dividindo-a em várias "
"páginas."

