#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave options"
msgstr "Configuração da Gravação Automática"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An autosave file is just a copy of your data file. The main point of these "
"is that they are automatically created, according to the configuration "
"settings, so you do not need to remember to take any action. Any autosave "
"files created will be in the same directory as the data file currently open."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Checking the <guilabel>Autosave periodically</guilabel> box instructs "
#| "&kmymoney; to autosave your files at a defined interval. The default "
#| "value is 10 minutes. You can change this setting from 0 (backup "
#| "immediately after entering a transaction) up to 60 minutes."
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Autosave periodically</guilabel> box instructs "
"&kmymoney; to automatically save your file at the interval defined by the "
"<guilabel>minutes</guilabel> field. The default value is 10 minutes. You can "
"change this setting from 0 (autosave immediately after entering a "
"transaction) up to 60 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Se assinalar a opção <guilabel>Auto-gravar periodicamente</guilabel>, "
"indicará ao &kmymoney; para gravar automaticamente os seus ficheiros com um "
"intervalo bem definido. O valor por omissão é de 10 minutos. Poderá alterar "
"esta configuração de 0 (gravar uma cópia imediatamente a seguir à introdução "
"de uma transacção) até 60 minutos."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Checking the <guilabel>Autosave when file is modified upon close</"
#| "guilabel> box instructs &kmymoney; to autosave your file when the program "
#| "is closed. You also have the option upon closing the program to backup "
#| "your &kmymoney; file. The Number of backup to keep can be set at 0 (Off) "
#| "upto to 20 backups. Any backup files will be stored in the same folder as "
#| "the main file. They will be labeled sequentially with 1 being the most "
#| "current."
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Autosave when file is modified upon close</guilabel> "
"box instructs &kmymoney; to autosave your file when the program is closed, "
"but only if any changes have been made. You also have the option upon "
"closing the program to backup your &kmymoney; file."
msgstr ""
"Se assinalar a opção <guilabel>Gravar automaticamente quando o ficheiro "
"estiver modificado ao fechar</guilabel>, irá indicar ao &kmymoney; para "
"gravar automaticamente o seu ficheiro quando fechar o programa. Terá também "
"a opção, quando fechar o programa, para gravar automaticamente o seu "
"ficheiro do &kmymoney;. O número de cópias de segurança a manter poderá ser "
"de 0 (Desligado) até 20 cópias de segurança. Essas cópias serão gravadas na "
"mesma pasta que o ficheiro principal. As mesmas serão registadas "
"sequencialmente, sendo que a 1 será a mais actual."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Number of backup to keep</guilabel> can be set from 0 (Off) up "
"to 20. The autosave files will be stored in the same folder as the main "
"file. If your data file is MyFinances.kmy, then when an autosave file is "
"created, it will be called MyFinances.kmy.1~. Any existing autosave files "
"will have their number increased by 1, up to the specified number."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fiscal Year"
msgstr "Ano Fiscal"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Enter the day and month of your fiscal year. This value is used for "
#| "budgets and some reports."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; allows you to specify a fiscal year different from the calendar "
"year. To do so, enter the day and month on which your fiscal year begins. "
"This value is used for budgets and some reports."
msgstr ""
"Indique o dia e o mês do seu ano fiscal. Este valor é usado para os "
"orçamentos e alguns relatórios."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "External programs"
msgstr "Programas externos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This setting does not directly affect the operation of &kmymoney;, but "
#| "provides a convenient way to launch any external utility, such as an "
#| "advanced calculator. The first step is to enter the full path to your "
#| "chosen program in the <guilabel>Calculator</guilabel> text box. There are "
#| "then two ways to launch the program."
msgid ""
"This setting does not directly affect the operation of &kmymoney;, but "
"provides a convenient way to launch any external utility, such as an "
"advanced calculator. The first step is to enter the full path to your chosen "
"program in the <guilabel>Calculator</guilabel> text box."
msgstr ""
"Esta opção não afecta a operação do &kmymoney;, mas oferece uma forma "
"conveniente de lançar qualquer utilitário externo, como uma calculadora "
"avançada. O primeiro passo é indicar a localização completa do seu programa "
"escolhido no campo de texto da <guilabel>Calculadora</guilabel>. Existem "
"assim duas formas de lançar o programa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is currently no direct menu item to launch the calculator, or whatever "
"external program you have set. There are then two ways to launch the program."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:111
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "First, you can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
#| "menu item to place the <guilabel>Calculator</guilabel> icon on the "
#| "Toolbar. Then, when you click that icon on the Toolbar, &kmymoney; will "
#| "launch the selected application."
msgid ""
"First, you can use <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem> menu item to place the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-accessories-"
"calculator.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Calculator icon on the Toolbar. Then, when you click that icon on "
"the Toolbar, &kmymoney; will launch the selected application."
msgstr ""
"Primeiro, pode usar a opção  <menuchoice><guimenu>Configuração</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configurar as Barras de Ferramentas...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> para colocar o ícone da <guilabel>Calculadora</guilabel> na "
"barra de ferramentas. Depois, poderá carregar nesse ícone na barra de "
"ferramentas. O &kmymoney; irá assim lançar a aplicação seleccionada."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:121
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Second, you can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
#| "menu item to set a custom keyboard shortcut. (The entry is under "
#| "&kmymoney;/Calculator in that list.) You can then use that shortcut to "
#| "launch the application."
msgid ""
"Second, you can use <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Shortcuts...</guimenuitem> menu item to set a custom keyboard shortcut. (The "
"entry is under &kmymoney;/Calculator in that list.) You can then use that "
"shortcut to launch the application."
msgstr ""
"Segundo, poderá usar a opção <menuchoice><guimenu>Configuração</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configurar os Atalhos...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"para definir um atalho de teclado personalizado. (O elemento encontra-se em "
"&kmymoney;/Calculadora nessa lista). Poderá então usar essa combinação de "
"teclas para lançar a aplicação."

